# 📘 Trainee Management API

##  Project Name

taskmanagement(TraineeManagement)

---

##  Technology Used
- C#
- ASP.NET Core Web API
- Entity Framework Core (InMemory Database)
- Swagger (OpenAPI)
- LINQ
- JSON

---

##  How to Run

1. Clone the repository
```
git clone https://github.com/smit2870/TrainingTasks.git  
cd taskmanagement
```

2. Run the project
```
dotnet run  
```

3. Open Swagger UI in browser:
```
https://localhost:7071/swagger  
```

---

##  API List

```
- GET /api/health  
- GET /api/trainees  
- GET /api/trainees/{id}  
- POST /api/trainees  
- PUT /api/trainees/{id}  
- DELETE /api/trainees/{id}  
- GET /api/trainees?search=smit  
```
---

##  Sample Request JSON
```
POST /api/trainees

{
  "firstName": "smit",
  "lastName": "patel",
  "email": "smit123a@gmail.com",
  "techStack": "HTML, CSS, JavaScript",
  "status": "Available"
}
```
---

##  Sample Response JSON

Success Response for Create and Get All Trainee Details.
```
{
  "id": 1,
  "firstName": "smit",
  "lastName": "patel",
  "email": "smit123@gmail.com",
  "techStack": "HTML, CSS, JavaScript",
  "status": "Available"
  "createdDate": "2026-06-08T10:45:38.3936817Z",
  "updatedDate": "2026-06-08T10:45:38.3936817Z"
}
```

Success Response for Get Trainee By Id and Changing Details(Put Request).
```
{
  "firstName": "smit",
  "lastName": "patel",
  "email": "smit123@gmail.com",
  "techStack": "HTML, CSS, JavaScript",
  "status": "Available"
  "updatedDate": "2026-06-08T10:45:38.3936817Z"
}
```
---


##  Known Limitations

- Uses EF Core InMemory Database (data resets on restart)
- No authentication or authorization
- Limited validation rules

---

##  Future Improvements

- Implement global error handling